{"tid":2173184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老十大特徵","createTime":"2020-08-25T05:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T14:32:11.000Z","uid":301952,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5680e6fcc49a5741cd8c1a6ae021eb9293f6c8b3","tid":2173184,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"1. 隨地吐痰，唔覺得係一種問題<br />\n2. 逼人食二手煙，唔覺得係一種問題<br />\n3. 覺得住公屋好自豪<br />\n4. 住私樓既永遠只想樓價gogogo，對社會實業發展無抱負<br />\n5. 我搵錢，社會成本係 WFC<br />\n6. 我死後，世界洪水滔天 WFC<br />\n7. 日本人係蘿蔔頭<br />\n8. 美帝忘我之心不死<br />\n9. 下一代叻過自己，寧願勾結支共消滅下一代，去滿足自己永遠叻過下一代既良好感覺<br />\n10. 明明睇過聽過笑聲救地球，表姐你好野，皇后大道東....明明係害怕支共怕九七既一代，對中港關係選擇性失憶"},{"pid":"e998d9591bc695856bbad9ef2a09f64d39deae33","tid":2173184,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:57:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6acf2f2fb0af65890097925b824d8f329c54b1cc","tid":2173184,"uid":201027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T06:01:22.000Z","msg":"狗奴才"},{"pid":"6c72300a7058db9fdab07a34327ccb2a29e8b6b5","tid":2173184,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T06:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df86d0a90ea441c3e0417d6573906c96e695a221","tid":2173184,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T06:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d840513f985e96989fcd1ff76442a6ce215b696f","tid":2173184,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T07:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ea952981a2df64567979509f8a304864e52dfb","tid":2173184,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T09:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid